title: Bug 6322 - All types dialog shows obfuscated classes
description: Bug 6322 - All types dialog shows obfuscated classes. JDK 1.4 includes obfuscated classes (a, a1, b, c, d) etc.
OB: The All types dialog is displaying the obfuscated classes prominently.
EB: The obfuscated classes should be displayed as less prominent or should not be displayed at all in the All types dialog.
SR: To reproduce the issue, open the All types dialog in JDK 1.4 and observe the display of obfuscated classes.
